docs.summary: Represents the icon button that closes the hamburger menu.
description: The hamburger close button is one of the components that exists within the hamburger menu container.
It is an icon button that closes the hamburger menu when clicked.
> **Note:** The hamburger menu can replace the traditional [Menu](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w/menu)
> to save space on smaller screen sizes. Its function is to toggle between a displayed and collapsed menu when triggered.
